---

This project builds upon SSO-Monitor:

  - GitHub:  https://github.com/RUB-NDS/SSO-Monitor
  - Website: https://sso-monitor.me/

We are building on SSO-Monitor with a substantial amount of changes to adapt
the framework for Passkey (WebAuthn) detection and analysis rather than
Single Sign-On (SSO).

